# CODEOWNERS for WannaBuild
#
# This file controls who is automatically requested as reviewer when a PR
# touches matching paths. Patterns are evaluated top-to-bottom; the LAST
# match wins (per GitHub's CODEOWNERS rules), so more-specific rules go
# below the catch-all.
#
# Currently @gl11tchy is the sole maintainer, so every path resolves to a
# single reviewer. PRs that touch sensitive surfaces (skills/, agents/,
# scripts/, schemas) MUST receive a maintainer review before merge — the
# `main` branch ruleset enforces required code-owner review.
#
# To propose adding a new maintainer or co-owner: open an issue using the
# "Specialist agent change" or "Contract or schema change" template (or a
# plain Discussion) describing scope, rationale, and the paths the new
# owner will cover. Maintainership additions are merged via a PR that
# updates this file plus docs/governance.md.

# Default owner — gl11tchy is the maintainer for everything not otherwise specified.
*                                       @gl11tchy

